---
// DemoVideo.astro — Format A Applied (Narrative + Visual)
---

<section id="demo-video" class="content-section">
  <div class="section-container">

    <!-- Title -->
    <h2 class="section-heading reveal">Real-World Experiment</h2>

    <!-- Intro (Format A style) -->
    <div class="prose reveal">
      <p>
        We have evaluated under real-world driving conditions with varying vibration levels and environmental complexity. 
        These experiments demonstrate how the system maintains perception fidelity, prioritizes informative data, and adapts 
        to challenging deployment scenarios.
      </p>
    </div>

    <!-- Highlights (Format A box) -->
    <div class="highlight-box reveal">

      <div class="highlight-item">
        <span class="highlight-number">🚗</span>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>Real Deployment</h4>
          <p>Evaluation on physical robotic vehicle under real driving conditions.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-item">
        <span class="highlight-number">⚡</span>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>Vibration Impact</h4>
          <p>Captures sensor degradation under unstable terrain and motion.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="highlight-item">
        <span class="highlight-number">📊</span>
        <div class="highlight-content">
          <h4>System Response</h4>
          <p>Demonstrates adaptive filtering and robust perception under stress.</p>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- Visual Grid (Refined A- style) -->
    <div class="media-grid reveal">

      <!-- Video -->
      <div class="media-item">
        <div class="video-container">
          <iframe
            src="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XJ6RTKSLHpggS11d33h5RUC6NltZzXkD/preview"
            allow="autoplay"
            allowfullscreen
            loading="lazy"
          ></iframe>
        </div>
        <div class="media-label">Real-world Data Collection</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image 1 -->
      <div class="media-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1_TBdIG1UbyEB6tQ_wzuksS9Ima-5Tifo" alt="Indoor setup"/>
        <div class="media-label">Indoor Testbed</div>
      </div>

      <!-- Image 2 -->
      <div class="media-item">
        <img src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/d/1J_BjOpYJwN7ZVhTn1hiGHkBT1WQkqpal" alt="Outdoor setup"/>
        <div class="media-label">Outdoor Testbed</div>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<style>

/* ===== TEXT ===== */
.prose p {
  font-size: 1.05rem;
  line-height: 1.8;
  color: #444;
  text-align: justify;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

/* ===== HIGHLIGHT BOX ===== */
.highlight-box {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.2rem;
  margin-bottom: 2rem;
}

.highlight-item {
  display: flex;
  gap: 0.8rem;
  padding: 1rem;
  border-left: 4px solid #c05e3c;
  background: rgba(0,0,0,0.02);
  border-radius: 10px;
  transition: all 0.25s ease;
}

.highlight-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-2px);
  box-shadow: 0 6px 18px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
}

.highlight-number {
  font-size: 1.2rem;
}

.highlight-content h4 {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 1rem;
  color: #223253;
}

.highlight-content p {
  margin: 0;
  font-size: 0.9rem;
}

/* ===== MEDIA GRID ===== */
.media-grid {
  display: grid;
  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
  gap: 1.5rem;
}

/* ===== CARD ===== */
.media-item {
  position: relative;
  border-radius: 14px;
  overflow: hidden;
  background: #111;
  aspect-ratio: 16 / 10;
  transition: all 0.3s ease;
}

.media-item:hover {
  transform: translateY(-6px);
  box-shadow: 0 12px 28px rgba(0,0,0,0.12);
}

/* ===== MEDIA ===== */
.media-item img,
.video-container iframe {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  object-fit: cover;
}

.video-container {
  width: 100%;
  height: 100%;
  position: relative;
}

/* ===== LABEL ===== */
.media-label {
  position: absolute;
  bottom: 0;
  left: 0;
  right: 0;
  padding: 0.9rem;
  font-size: 0.85rem;
  color: white;
  background: linear-gradient(transparent, rgba(0,0,0,0.85));
  letter-spacing: 0.5px;
}

/* ===== RESPONSIVE ===== */
@media (max-width: 768px) {
  .prose p {
    text-align: left;
  }
}

</style>